Your friends cannot see the instance you are in. They may request to join, but you will not receive any notifications. In fact, you won't be able to send or request any invites to your friends within the game if they are in that status.
* Incoming friend requests are delivered quietly to the "Friend Requests" Inbox.
* A response for a request (ex. invite request) you send out, will be displayed.
* Group notifications are disabled.